# File Handling
The process of working with files in a program. It involves opening, reading, writing, and closing files.

# File Handling useCases
- Read data
- Append data
- Write data
- Create files
- Delete files

# Opening  and Clsoing files
#open file
file = open("myfile.txt", "r") # r for read, w for write

#close file
file.close()

# Reading file data
#open file
file = open("myfile.txt", "r")

#Read the contents of the file
contents = file.read()

#print the fiel contents
print(contents)

#close file
file.close()
